        Thanks for picking up a copy, I hope you‚Äôre enjoying it! As for getting up to 30 FPS is challenging, but it is possible. I would suggest starting here and reading up on how threading can improve your FPS processing rate. You‚Äôll also want to keep your frames as small as possible without sacrificing accuracy. The smaller the frames are, the less data there is to process, thus your pipeline will run faster.
